our Ghouls. If you use a level 8 spell slot, you can animate or reassert control over five Ghouls or two Ghasts or Wights. If you use a level 9 spell slot, you can animate or reassert control over six Ghouls, three Ghasts or Wights, or two Mummies"}, "classes": {"value": ["cleric", "warlock", "wizard"]}, "dice": {"value": []}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.649890"}, "id": "create_undead"}}, {"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "spell", "stats": {"name": {"value": "Finger of Death"}, "source": {"value": "phb"}, "level": {"value": "spell_level_7"}, "school": {"value": "spell_school_necromancy"}, "casting_time": {"value": "1 action"}, "range": {"value": "60 feet"}, "duration": {"value": "Instantaneous"}, "verbal": {"value": true}, "somatic": {"value": true}, "description": {"value": "You unleash negative energy toward a creature you can see within range. The target makes a Constitution saving throw, taking 7d8 + 30 Necrotic damage on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one.\n\nA Humanoid killed by this spell rises at the start of your next turn as a Zombie that follows your verbal orders"}, "classes": {"value": ["sorcerer", "warlock", "wizard"]}, "dice": {"value": [{"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "levelled_damage_dice", "stats": {"level": {"value": 7}, "damage_dice": {"value": [{"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "damage_dice", "stats": {"dices": {"value": [{"system": "5e2024", "resource_id": "dice_roll", "stats": {"dice_amount": {"value": 7}, "dice_type": {"value": "d8"}, "constant": {"value": 30}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.644324"}, "id": "d3c028ee-dbea-458b-bde5-0b854b1a840f"}}]}, "damage_type": {"value": "necrotic"}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.644330"}, "id": "02c6d17d-5424-4147-a2f7-de1f49aa7f19"}}]}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.644335"}, "id": "3531229d-67f3-4fb3-b186-262eb0d4cfd5"}}]}, "updated_at": {"value": "2024-12-20T18:50:46.644338"}, "id": "finger_of_death"}}]}, "habit